{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_01","textHome":"我从第一次来神滨的时候就感觉有些……违和。@乍一看，好像和我们住的见泷原没什么区别，@但空气中的魔力波动，和见泷原的完全不同。@不早不晚，就是那个时候感觉到的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200500}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_18","textHome":"我最喜欢的魔法……应该是做红茶的魔法吧。@战斗结束之后，能够休息一下就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200500}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_19","textHome":"感觉自己跨越了界限。我还能更强吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_20","textHome":"我看到了……在我心中广阔的景色……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_21","textHome":"虽然我在成为魔法少女的时候，@没心思考虑活下去以外的愿望。@但如果有机会的话，@我又会怎么做呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200500,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_22","textHome":"过去我一直都是一个人在战斗。@作为魔法少女的烦恼辛苦还有害怕，@没法和任何人坦白，一直独自一人……@但是，现在我有了同伴……@所以我能够坚持下去……这是毋庸置疑的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_23","textHome":"和同伴一起战斗的时候特别安心、幸福。@这是一个人战斗的时候所感受不到的。@有和自己心意相通的人存在，@真是一件非常幸运的事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200500}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200500,"motion"